parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents or near-misses, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake light on the dashboard illuminates
grinding or screeching noises are heard when applying the brakes
the brake pedal travels to the floor
the vehicle vibrates or pulsates when braking
and the brakes may fail to operate or respond slowly.
